国就在身后<br />\n远方传来敌军的脚步声 大地在颤抖<br />\n是捍卫正义的时候了 热血早已澎湃<br />\n干枯树枝上最后一片树叶被寒风打落</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">闪电撕破了远处承重的黑幕 看 是SS部队在前进</span><br />\n<br />\nThe Mass曾一度被認為改編自「德國黨衛軍第一裝甲師軍歌」，即所謂的《閃電部隊在前進》。 究其原因，大概是<span style=\"color: red;\">納粹首領希特勒</span>非常喜歡《布蘭詩歌》，所以有可能把《哦！命運女神》的曲子作為了SS裝甲擲彈師軍歌的曲調。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁多首歌唔用，支那帝吧徧要用咁撚重納粹色彩既歌？ 當左自己係SS黨衞軍？？？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝帝吧送彈藥！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"《The Mass》是新世紀音樂團體ERA在2003年推出的第三張音樂專輯。<br />\n<br />\n專輯內的同名歌曲《The Mass》在中國被誤認為是二戰時期德國納粹黨衛軍第一裝甲師的軍歌，並翻譯為《閃電部隊在行動》或《SS閃電部隊在行動》。<br />\n-- from wiki"},{"pid":"024f79423e090b4311cd3781df725c7bb37596f5","tid":1491871,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\n<br />\n班仆街唔係用The Mass<br />\n<br />\n而係直接用左Panzerlied"},{"pid":"b0a13148f5a4ba518dbee54ccdc788fbc218cad7","tid":1491871,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2f109b9e46bb7e7aefb6462305a5002e303b80e","tid":1491871,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"909f2ac42740b9942b1d6d62e10c94e5d74a5b62","tid":1491871,"uid":302320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"612<br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"01c6dedf3712ed5b2a2c5f1f9b01880df23d0b68","tid":1491871,"uid":302320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:53:25.000Z","msg":"推上Twitter<br />\n#chinazism"},{"pid":"80b9c70764ae724fde1de3cb4cb14ee5e9132382","tid":1491871,"uid":310682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:58:46.000Z","msg":"其實大陸人可能連nazi係咩都唔知<br />\n可能nazi都weibo唔到"},{"pid":"3c5a12e06dad9f28a264b1e82e5e31106